<Card title="Technique Guides" description="Learn amazing street workout and calisthenics skills" img={exerciseImg} leftColor="#A74CF2" rightColor="#617BFB" /> <br/> <Card title="Skills Training" description="Learn amazing street workout and calisthenics skills" img={exerciseImg} leftColor="blue" rightColor="seagreen" /> </div> ) } } export default Exercises
